## Page Structure

### Authentication Flow

- **`/login`** - Login and signup page with Firebase authentication
  - Supports email/password and Google OAuth
  - Toggle between login and signup modes
  - Redirects to `/canvas` on successful authentication

### Main Application

- **`/canvas`** - Main collaborative canvas interface
  - Protected route requiring authentication
  - Single collaborative canvas with real-time synchronization
  - Displays connection status and online users
  - Canvas implementation using Konva for 2D graphics
  - Shape creation tools with database persistence
  - Real-time collaborative editing
  - User avatar and navigation components

### State Management

- **`store/user-store.ts`** - Zustand store for user authentication state
- **`store/canvas-store.ts`** - Zustand store for canvas state management
- **`store/cursor-store.ts`** - Zustand store for cursor state management
- **`lib/firebase/`** - Firebase configuration and authentication setup
- **`types/index.ts`** - TypeScript type definitions and interfaces
- **`lib/canvas-service.ts`** - Canvas database operations and real-time sync
- **`services/shapeTransactions.ts`** - Shape transaction service for database operations

